choices.text:
travelling for the sake of travelling. That’s not what travelling is about. It’s about self-discovery, growing through the process of learning about someone and themselves.

…I just don’t have a speech here in general. I can see rivers of love but if they don’t come from the well within us we let them all slip through the cracks here and there.

You are so trapped in your own views of what is and what isn’t, that what isn’t coming your way cannot seem to arrive. And this ignorance…is your own pettiness. To be hung up on your views and how things should be without a shread of reason…is twisted. To love so much but have nothing to give is the power that hurts the most.

i see many spreading darkness and painting everytging black as reigniting a flame of darkness…i feel the echo of the light, and it’s all around us (angels)…we’re keep on being in the spotlight…

You can’t please everyone so don’t even try.

As woman it is as important as peace of mind…
